#, no-c-format
msgid "Synopsis"
msgstr "简介"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>meinproc6</command> <arg choice=\"opt\">-h, --help</arg> <arg "
"choice=\"opt\">-v, --version</arg> <arg choice=\"opt\">--cache<replaceable> "
"file</replaceable></arg> <arg choice=\"opt\">--check</arg> <arg "
"choice=\"opt\">--srcdir<replaceable> dir</replaceable></arg> <arg "
"choice=\"opt\">--param <replaceable>key</replaceable>=<replaceable>value</"
"replaceable></arg> <group> <group> <arg>-o</arg> <arg>--output</arg> </"
"group> <replaceable> file</replaceable> </group> <arg choice=\"opt\">--"
"stdout</arg> <arg choice=\"opt\">--stylesheet<replaceable> xsl</"
"replaceable></arg> <arg choice=\"plain\">docbook_file</arg>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>meinproc6</command> converts DocBook files to &HTML;."
msgstr "<command>meinproc6</command> 将 DocBook 文件转换为 &HTML;。"

#. Tag: title
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Generic Options"
msgstr "常规选项"

#. Tag: term
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-h</option><option>--help</option>"
msgstr "<option>-h</option><option>--帮助</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show help about options."
msgstr "显示帮助关于选项."

#. Tag: term
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-v</option><option>--version</option>"
msgstr "<option>-v</option><option>--版本</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show version information."
msgstr "显示版本信息。"

#. Tag: title
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application Options"
msgstr "应用程序选项"

#. Tag: term
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--cache</option> <parameter>file</parameter>"
msgstr "<option>--缓存</option> <parameter>文件</parameter>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a cache file for the document."
msgstr "为文档创建缓存文件。"

#. Tag: option
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "--check"
msgstr "--check"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check the document for validity."
msgstr "检查文档是否有效。"

#. Tag: screen
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The output can be a bit daunting, since one small mistake can cause a "
"cascade of errors. \n"
"The trick is to look at the first error, fix that error, save the file, and "
"run <command>meinproc6</command> again."
msgstr ""
"输出可能看起来有点可怕，因为一个小错误可能会造成一连串错误。 \n"
"技巧是查看第一个错误，并修复那个错误，然后保存文件，并重新运行 "
"<command>meinproc6</command>"

#. Tag: term
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-o</option>, <option>--output</option><parameter> file</parameter>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-o</option>, <option>--输出</option><parameter>文件</parameter>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "Output whole document to <parameter>file</parameter>."
msgstr "输出整个文档到 <parameter>文件</parameter>"

#. Tag: option
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "--stdout"
msgstr "--stdout"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "Output whole document to stdout."
msgstr "输出整个文档到 stdout 。"

#. Tag: term
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--stylesheet</option> <parameter>xsl</parameter>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stylesheet to use."
msgstr "要使用的样式表。"

#. Tag: term
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--srcdir</option> <parameter>dir</parameter>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the root directory to look for kdoctools."
msgstr "设置要查找 kdoctools 的根目录。"

#. Tag: term
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--param</option> key=value"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set parameters to pass to the stylesheet."
msgstr "设置要传递到样式表的参数。"

#. Tag: title
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "用途"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most common way to run <command>meinproc6</command> is simply as "
"<literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> <replaceable>docbook-file</"
"replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> where <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable> is usually "
"index.docbook. This command creates &HTML; pages from the DocBook file. Note "
"that these pages are only viewable in &kde;-based browsers (like "
"&konqueror;)."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you need to view the &HTML; output in another browser (for example, if "
"you're placing it on line), use <literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> --stylesheet <replaceable>stylesheet-"
"name</replaceable> <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> where <replaceable>stylesheet-name</replaceable> is the "
"full path to one of the &XSL; stylesheets in "
"&lt;kdoctools_installation_prefix&gt;/share/kf5/kdoctools/customization/. To "
"produce output suitable for the web, you can use <command>kde-web.xsl</"
"command> or <command>kde-chunk-online.xsl</command>. See the "
"<filename>README</filename> file in that directory for more details."
msgstr ""
"如果您需要使用其他浏览器（比如您需要把它放在网上）查看&HTML;输出，请使用"
"<literallayout><userinput><command>meinproc6</command> --stylesheet "
"<replaceable>stylesheet-name</replaceable> <replaceable>docbook-file</"
"replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout><replaceable>stylesheet-name</replaceable>是 /share/kf5/"
"kdoctools/customization/"
"&lt;kdoctools_installation_prefix&gt;&lt;kdoctools_installation_prefix&gt;&lt;kdoctools_installation_prefix&gt; "
"内某一样式表的完整路径。要生成适合网络的输出，您可以使用 <command>kde-"
"web.xsl</command> 或 <command>kde-chunk-online.xsl</command> 。在那个目录中阅"
"读 <filename>README</filename> 文件以了解更多详情。"

